data.description: Splendid ranch style 3-bedroom, 2 full bath home just minutes away from Blue Angel Parkway, Naval Air Station Pensacola and the beautiful beaches of Perdido Key.    With updates, a 2021 roof, luxury vinyl plank floor throughout, slate-grey kitchen appliances and ceiling fans for energy efficiency; this charming home is ready for its new family.    The living room has a wood burning fireplace, great for large get-togethers and seasonal celebrations. The backyard is spacious, fenced and perfect for outdoor activities or time with pets.   OPEN HOUSE: You’re warmly invited to our open house festivity Saturday and Sunday, January 13th and 14th, from 12PM to 5PM. Let’s make it an evening to remember.
